Package ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.AssetTrading.Deprecated

Class OrganisationalUnitMembers

java.lang.Object
ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.AssetTrading.Deprecated.User
ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.AssetTrading.Deprecated.OrganisationalUnitMembers
public class OrganisationalUnitMembers
extends User
OrganisationalUnitMembers class which extends the user class. This class is implemented for users who wish to trade their organisational unit's assets by connecting to the server and managing unit asset listings via their client side GUI.
